  "texts": [
    "For details see SI13.",
    "The generative deep learning method referred to as DRAGONFLY was evaluated in the context of ligand-based and structure-based molecular design tasks.",
    "The collective results specifically highlight the success of structure-based de novo design of potent partial agonizts for PPARγ.",
    "These molecules effectively interact with the receptor in a canonical binding mode, while also demonstrating the desired selectivity towards the receptor and favorable ADME properties.",
    "By leveraging an interactome-based deep learning approach and employing a graph-to-sequence neural network architecture, DRA-GONFLY addresses certain challenges commonly encountered in generative molecular design methods."
